Package: ESImap
Title: Spatial Analysis and Neighborhood Mapping for HALO Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ramin", "Herati", "ramin.herati@nyulangone.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A specialized toolset for processing HALO imaging data using Giotto. 
    It provides advanced workflows for data integration, niche composition analysis, 
    and neighborhood-dependent feature expression testing.
